1
00:00:04,147 --> 00:00:06,601
When we say, 
“These higher devotees …”

2
00:00:06,901 --> 00:00:09,985
They are not meditating

3
00:00:09,985 --> 00:00:13,356
as people conventionally
think of meditation.

4
00:00:13,356 --> 00:00:18,469
When they are in the inner world
they’re rendering seva.

5
00:00:18,469 --> 00:00:20,267
It’s not that they
are just thinking
 

6
00:00:20,267 --> 00:00:23,267
about something 
that’s pleasing to them.

7
00:00:23,267 --> 00:00:25,978
Bhajan means direct service,

8
00:00:25,978 --> 00:00:29,638
They are serving 
in that plane.

9
00:00:29,638 --> 00:00:33,174
It’s not just having 
a glimpse of view

10
00:00:33,174 --> 00:00:38,842
of some extraordinary, 
divine …

11
00:00:38,842 --> 00:00:42,332
what do they say,
what’s the word?

12
00:00:42,332 --> 00:00:45,010
Environment, but scene …
Avadhūt Mahārāj: reality.
 

13
00:00:45,010 --> 00:00:49,090
Goswami Mahārāj: yeah,
but they’re serving there.

14
00:00:49,090 --> 00:00:51,652
So, he says in that world

15
00:00:51,652 --> 00:00:54,469
to the devotee 
at his side in this world,

16
00:00:54,469 --> 00:00:59,729
he’s saying,
he’s giving him a commend 
 

17
00:01:00,120 --> 00:01:03,820
of some service 
to do in that plane,

18
00:01:03,970 --> 00:01:05,990
and it also has to do

19
00:01:05,990 --> 00:01:08,990
with not allowing 
any disturbance

20
00:01:08,990 --> 00:01:14,530
to come in the pastimes 
of Rādhā-Mukunda.

